         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">19/4/87 ¶  ¶ Your kind announcement, dear Prof Abbot, of my election, reached me only quite recently, along with some publications from various places of the U.S. through some channel unknown to me; s...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">87.04.19c</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Samuel Abbot</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Incoming correspondence, Boston Society of Natural History papers, Museum of Science, Boston.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See also M to S. Abbot, 19 April 1887 (in this edition as 87-04-19b).</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>19/4/87</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your kind announcement, dear Prof Abbot, of my election, reached me only quite recently, along with some publications from various places of the U.S. through some channel unknown to me; so that I cannot say, where the detention occurred. Thus my tardy acknowledgement will be excused. If you wrote to the excellent Mr. George Davis, Medical Publisher at Detroit, that liberal Gentleman, would be sure to send you a copy of his American edition of my "select plants for industrial culture and naturalisation."<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B84.13.22.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I send your Society for kind acceptance by <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">this post</hi>
               </seg>:</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">a quarto-volume of illustrations of myoporinous plants (the text will appear next year);<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B86.13.21. The promised text volume was not published.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">—<seg style=""> </seg>also my system "Census of Austral. plants" with three supplements.<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B82.13.16, B84.13.16, B85.13.19, B86.06.03.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> Let me kindly know, whether all reached you safely and free. My departmental stamp franks to the U.S.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd von Mueller.</p>
